comment: Favors (UTA) is in a legal guarding position on the handoff. Thomas (NYK) runs into him while trying to chase his man over the screen.
RHH shows contact between Galloway (NYK) and Hood (UTA) is slight and does not affect Hood's RSBQ.
Gobert (UTA) jumps vertically to contest Galloway's (NYK) layup attempt. Players must jump vertically and maintain their up and down trajectory. However, contact may turn the defender in the air.
LO_SLA shows Ingles (UTA) makes contact with Aldrich's (NYK) wrist, which prevents him from controlling the rebound. A loose ball foul is assessed because Aldrich did not have possession.

Favors (UTA) has his arm extended when Bargnani (NYK) attempts a "rip through." Since Bargnani is moving side-to-side, he is not considered to have started his upward shooting motion and a personal foul is assessed.
Shved (NYK) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Hood (UTA) .
Exum (UTA) cleanly knocks the ball away from Galloway (NYK) as he catches the outlet pass.
Ingles (UTA) does not have possession when he attempts to gain control of the ball and therefore he doesn't establish a pivot foot before he spins and passes.
RHH shows Favors (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position as Bargnani(NYK) drives to basket. Bargnani makes space when Favors doesn't yield his defensive position.
Contact between Aldrich (NYK) and Gobert (UTA) is incidental in their attempt to gain the rebound.
Shved (NYK) commits a take foul on Burke (UTA).
Exum (UTA) draws Shved (NYK) into the air and makes contact as he begins his upward shooting motion.
Shved (NYK) commits a take foul on Burke (UTA).
